text: Yummy yummy food in my tummy. Came here for dinner and enjoyed it. Also, members get to redeem a free drink for every $50 spent

Very spacious but wish there was a lot more ice cream flavours, pretty limited and most of them are the usual ones. The waffle exterior is slightly crispy and can be more crispy while the inside is a little soggy.

Tucked at  quite corner in Bedok Reservoir, where Chuan HKM is located at the next block. Located at a block near bus stop and parking was easy. We were able to get seats for lunch on a Sunday easily. Food was good, service fast as well. Would recommend if you Re around the area. Thank you
